Share this on WhatsAppSpread the lovePopular aphrodisiac seller, Jaruma, has offered actress, Chacha Eke-Faani and her kids a home, after the latter announced the end of her marriage.
On Tuesday, Eke-Faani, announced on Instagram that her marriage was over saying, “For the second time in two years, I am here again on social media boldly declaring that I am done with my marriage.”
In reaction, Jaruma put up a post on her Instagram page stating how women don’t have places to go to when they leave their men.
Jaruma said, “When we leave our men, we normally don’t have a place to stay. Chacha you can stay in one of my houses with your kids before I get a buyer. Sending you love, light & support.”
